OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780989358
OL,3,CWarning issued after child seen
OL,4,Callegedly holding onto back of running
OL,5,Ctram
OL,7,FThe operator that runs Nottingham's
OL,8,Ftrams has issued a warning after a
OL,9,Fyoung person was allegedly spotted
OL,10,Fholding onto the back of a moving tram.
OL,12,FA picture posted on social media on
OL,13,FThursday, June 4, appeared to showed a
OL,14,Fyouth clinging to a tram in Beeston
OL,15,Fwhile it was in motion.
OL,17,FThe behaviour has been described as
OL,18,F"extremely dangerous" by Nottingham
OL,19,FExpress Transit.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780989358
OL,3,CWarning issued after child seen
OL,4,Callegedly holding onto back of running
OL,5,Ctram
OL,7,FAndy Downie, head of operations and
OL,8,Fsafety at NET said: "We're aware of an
OL,9,Fincident in Beeston that took place
OL,10,Finvolving a young person holding onto
OL,11,Fthe back of a tram while it was in
OL,12,Fmotion.
OL,14,F"Although this was an isolated
OL,15,Fincident, we would like to remind
OL,16,Fpeople that interfering with the tram
OL,17,Fis extremely dangerous and can have
OL,18,Fvery serious consequences that could
OL,19,Fresult in death or serious injury.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780989358
OL,3,CWarning issued after child seen
OL,4,Callegedly holding onto back of running
OL,5,Ctram
OL,7,F"The safety of all our tram users, our
OL,8,Ftram drivers and the people of
OL,9,FNottingham will always be our
OL,10,Fpriority, and we don't take such
OL,11,Fincidents lightly.
OL,13,F"Anyone caught engaging in dangerous
OL,14,Factivities such as this, will face the
OL,15,Frepercussions of their actions and
OL,16,Fwill be reported to the police."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
